title: Charming 2 Bedroom View of Golden Gate Bridge on Pacific and Baker
posting_body: ['Address: 2988 Pacific Ave, #5, San Francisco CA 94115', 'Neighborhood: Pacific Heights', 'Bedrooms: 2', 'Bathrooms: 2', 'Style: Apartment', 'Parking: Street', 'Security Deposit: $13,500', 'Lease Term: 12 months', 'Rent: $11,500', 'No Pet', 'This beautiful Penthouse home, located in upper Pac-Heights, has been fully renovated with new cabinets, countertops, and a wine bar.', 'You have a direct view of the Golden Gate Bridge and can relax on your private rooftop deck.', 'This home comes with a full-size washer and dryer, garage parking and an extra storage room, which can be used as an office.', 'FEATURES:', '•Elegant Lobby', '•In Unit Washer/Driver', '•Gas Fireplace', '•Driveway Parking Spot', '•Garage for additional storage, small office or parking', '•Additional storage or small office space off of the garage', '•Your Own Private Patio', '•Owner pays: Water and Garbage', 'REQUIREMENTS:', 'Credit: Good Standing', 'Income: 3x the Rent', 'Guarantors Accepted', 'Security Deposit Required', 'Application Fee: $45 per applicant', 'Lease Terms: Annual', 'TO VIEW THIS UNIT', 'PLEASE CONTACT:', 'Leasing Department', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', '<URL>', 'Professionally Managed by Chandler Properties', '*This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.', '*']
